### Part 2: Client-Side Utility

#### 2A. Update `client/src/utils/getShareUrl.js`

Add a new exported function `getProfileShareUrl`:

```js
export const getProfileShareUrl = (username) => {
    const backendUrl = import.meta.env.VITE_BACKEND_URL?.trim();
    const base = backendUrl
        ? backendUrl.replace(/\/+$/, '')
        : `${window.location.origin}/api`;
    return `${base}/share/u/${encodeURIComponent(username)}`;
};
```

Keep the existing default export `getShareUrl` unchanged for backward compatibility.

